# Documenting entity modeling changes

Any change to CSV schemas, columns, slug semantics, or relationships between `races`, `distances`, `types`, and `providers` **must** be reflected in `/docs` (at minimum `docs/data-model.md`, and add or update a focused doc such as `docs/slug-conventions.md` when slug rules change).

Do not change entity shape in code or data without updating the documentation in the same change.
